  <header>

    <div class="row collapse">

      <div class="twelve columns end">
        
          
            <h3 class="title" itemprop="title"><a href="http://www.fastcocreate.com/3042546/art-imagination-and-award-show-history-dominate-the-oscars-ad-campaign" title="Art, Imagination, And Award Show History Dominate The Oscars Ad Campaign" data-event-category="river" data-event-action="clickTitle">Art, Imagination, And Award Show History Dominate The Oscars Ad Campaign</a></h3>
          
        
      </div>


     

      <div class="eleven columns end">
        <span class="teaser" itemprop="teaser">
          
            <p>As the industry primps for its glamour close-up, the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences focuses on the power of imagination.</p>
          
        </span>

        
        
          
